ite係唔難，但一陣個site死左/有security問題就未必個個識處理"},{"pid":"5b974399fbc5c1dcaabef374a6f4a8c4d3e90738","tid":1891772,"uid":240740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e0b0b9f60e28a85c671c18d0239f4eded561571","tid":1891772,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90146c9da2b44abaca491571e30ec9e2b76c6020","tid":1891772,"uid":104138,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"39f29182ee858811acee69043b790ec6c1317713","tid":1891772,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"如果只係自己一個run嘅online shop <br />\n要開BR，公司bank acc，申請trademark...<br />\n仲有冇？<br />\n<br />\n呢類文件好難睇 唔識搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd稅收嗰d係點計？<br />\n<br />\n呢d野有冇得請個人幫我搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T06:06:42.000Z","msg":"成立有限公司後要查冊之後註冊<br />\n搞BR<br />\n公司bank account你無返十零廿萬大銀行唔會理你<br />\ntrademark你係nobody又無閒錢唔駛申請住<br />\n有公司會一站式幫你搞<br />\n<br />\n另外就係technical 果part，你搞online shop一係搵人幫你寫<br />\n一係你自己整/寫<br />\n前者你預返 5-30萬筆直，睇你想做到幾複雜，質素有幾高<br />\n後者不外乎用wix, shopify , magento, wordpress 如果你有coding底可以用你自己熟既language 寫但勸你咪搞咁多野<br />\n最後hosting 因應返你用咩solution整<br />\n<br />\n最後d 數要record清楚，單同收據有晒copy ，每年可以搵d 會計師行幫你搞報稅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"好詳細<br />\n唔該晒！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n報稅嗰part係一年搵會計師行一次就ok？<br />\n有冇話通常係幾月要開始搵？<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思好多問題<br />\n因為我完全冇business底<br />\n啱啱grad自己想開店 咩都唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:20:59.000Z","msg":"報稅係一年一次，幾時揾就要睇你公司year end係幾時，香港多數公司都係每年3月31號（跟香港tax year）或者12月31號<br />\n<br />\n不過其實你一個人搞online shop我諗條數都唔會好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以自己報稅都OK，最緊要做好record keeping，留單留invoice<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝你創業成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗唔好意思，我都係岩岩grad，雖然唔知你賣咩，不過你開得店證明你呢方面嘅skills已經好好，又會不恥下問，已經成功咗一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cce0930da15c9a34b4ac6236d191c0dbc4ef9cf","tid":1891772,"uid":167289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05f7e553b042752fd311e731f1032cb969967863","tid":1891772,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63bb2416b2fa7ab50232faa38bf0a0b52d352ad5","tid":1891772,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79f178df91902b84910049a540d633012b0ff4be","tid":1891772,"uid":296589,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"online shop一般會用MySQL database 做產品資料庫.<br />\n去Godaddy申請Domain Name, hosting含MySQL個種,再申請SSL安全證.<br />\n最簡單用Wordpress+online shop插件.<br />\n先係自己電腦localhost安裝WAMP, WAMP内含phpmyadmin(MySQL)<br />\n砌好個site再upload上hosting"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:33:40.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打解答 但我一句都睇唔明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家用緊shopline砌<br />\n我見佢唔難用 同埋可以駁去順豐發貨"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:45:52.000Z","msg":"睇Youtube,好多教學片<br />\nShopline都好,但收USD1700一年.<br />\n自己學識hosting就唔駛HK$1000一年.而且完全冇限制,亦可以無限開店.<br />\n不過要學識亦不是一時3刻. 將精力放係銷售亦是好的."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:24:53.000Z","msg":"就算識coding 自己整個購物網都唔係咁簡單喎<br />\n人哋shopline shopify嗰啲乜都optimize晒<br />\n唔駛自己左試右試"},{"pid":"0a2d173a13ef94f9659cf544a61661c5d136e67d","tid":1891772,"uid":108158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:32:03.000Z","msg":"而家銀行開新公司户口都幾嚴，之前試過行山，東亞都唔批俾我。。"},{"pid":"16071895b901534b917bf35ff9849570947b07e2","tid":1891772,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac570a069e54e7281596b2f39609546a0829f532","tid":18917