/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝你創業成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗唔好意思，我都係岩岩grad，雖然唔知你賣咩，不過你開得店證明你呢方面嘅skills已經好好，又會不恥下問，已經成功咗一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T19:10:07.000Z","msg":"我連報稅個format係點都唔知<br />\n第一年請人搞先<br />\n之後如果覺得handle到可以自己做埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<br />\n我賣下d手工嘢咋<br />\n創業唔容易 但都想試下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜鬼嘢不恥下問吖<br />\n根本就係咩都唔識要請教大家<br />\n多謝你地解答就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faabc431c9aafe3c332853406b18d4e0c42b0126","tid":1891772,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a2d173a13ef94f9659cf544a61661c5d136e67d","tid":1891772,"uid":108158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T18:32:03.000Z","msg":"而家銀行開新公司户口都幾嚴，之前試過行山，東亞都唔批俾我。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T19:11:03.000Z","msg":"想問下係點解唔批？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3315a7408a7d223de9087c6c8d8b5f19c42d796","tid":1891772,"uid":161168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T19:14:41.000Z","msg":"月收幾多先"},{"pid":"47fc60c8eb6a363a60d6ba728b589ae2f6e271b4","tid":1891772,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cce0930da15c9a34b4ac6236d191c0dbc4ef9cf","tid":1891772,"uid":167289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05f7e553b042752fd311e731f1032cb969967863","tid":1891772,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63bb2416b2fa7ab50232faa38bf0a0b52d352ad5","tid":1891772,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:33:40.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打解答 但我一句都睇唔明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl